				<div class="hvres-meaning">Âm Pinyin: <a href="/py/zi4">zì <span class="small gray han">ㄗˋ</span></a><br/>Âm Nôm: <a href="/nom/tí">tí</a>, <a href="/nom/xế">xế</a><br/>Âm Nhật (onyomi): <a href="/reading/1/1/セ">セ (se)</a>, <a href="/reading/1/1/イシ">イシ (ishi)</a>, <a href="/reading/1/1/サイ">サイ (sai)</a>, <a href="/reading/1/1/シ">シ (shi)</a>, <a href="/reading/1/1/セイ">セイ (sei)</a><br/>Âm Nhật (kunyomi): <a href="/reading/1/2/まなじり">まなじり (manajiri)</a>, <a href="/reading/1/2/めじり">めじり (mejiri)</a><br/>Âm Hàn: <a href="/reading/1/3/자">자</a>, <a href="/reading/1/3/제">제</a><br/>Âm Quảng Đông: <a href="/reading/1/4/zaai6">zaai6</a>, <a href="/reading/1/4/zi6">zi6</a></div><p class="hvres-source">Tự hình <span class="badge">1</span></p>
